---
title: Festive Herb Crusted Salmon with Cheesy Smashed Potatoes and Cranberry Balsamic Sprouts
description: Serve up a festive feast this winter! Make a meal that's truly special with this lightly indulgent and luxurious Festive Herb Crusted Salmon.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R35_W51_UK_SS17752-3_Main_high-d9634924.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/652e71256720825b47fd9fee.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
nutrition:
